longBusinessSummary: Global Seed Corporation provides coffee and healthy beverage products under the Ka Su Le brand name in China. The company engages in the wholesale, retail, and online sale of coffee and beverage items comprising capsules of coffee and non-coffee drinks through its Brand Stores; coffee brewing machines for domestic and commercial use; and various health supplements and skin care products. As of October 8, 2020, it operated seven stores in Guangdong Province, Jilin Province, and Chongqing City. Global Seed Corporation is headquartered in Dongguan, China.
